scene.message:
Nanjo: We have quite some{nl}
time before the exam.{nl}
Let's visit Sonohara first.{nl}
Waste not.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Tch, cold as always...{nl}
...Sonohara's in{nl}
room 302.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Huh, Inaba,{nl}
you sure know{nl}
your way around.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: ...Shut it.{nl}
A friend told me, okay?{nl}
Come on, {ctl0f:1}, let's go.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Hospitals really do{nl}
make you wait.{nl}
It seems they've never{nl}
heard "time is money."{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: ...What is it.{nl}
Quit staring at me{nl}
and get moving.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Huh...{nl}
Inaba knowing Sonohara's{nl}
room number — who'd have{nl}
thought it.{waitkey}{ret}

Nurse: Hm? Sonohara Maki?{nl}
Oh, her...{nl}
Maki's in room 302.{waitkey}{ret}

Yamaoka: Oh no, you found{nl}
me!{waitkey}Please don't tell{nl}
the young master{nl}
I was here...{waitkey}{ret}

College Girl: This is bad...{nl}
Hey, do you know{nl}
where the police station is?{nl}
My friend crashed his bike...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Hey, what's going on?{nl}
Police? You mean that{nl}
knucklehead's place?{nl}
Head west on Mikage Blvd.{waitkey}{ret}

College Girl: The main road —{nl}
you mean the one south{nl}
of here? Thanks a lot.{waitkey}{ret}

Pregnant Woman: I wonder if{nl}
my husband is okay...{nl}
Having hallucinations at{nl}
work — early burnout?{waitkey}{ret}

Salaryman: I'm going to work!{nl}
So what if the hall and{nl}
stairs are illusions!{nl}
So what if there's a ghost{waitkey}{clearbox}of a dark girl!{nl}
A SEBEC employee{nl}
can't let that stop them!{nl}
For real!{waitkey}{ret}

Injured Man: Ow ow ow...{nl}
Getting an accident report{nl}
is such a hassle...{nl}
just my luck.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Hey, hey...{nl}
you gonna visit{nl}
Sonohara or what?{nl}
Cold-hearted jerk.{waitkey}{ret}
